sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Owner->>Frontend: Open workspace members modal
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/workspaces/{id}/members
    API->>API: Validate JWT and workspace access
    API->>DB: Load workspace members
    DB-->>API: Member list
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + members
    Frontend-->>Owner: Display members modal
